---
layout: base.njk
title: "Portfolio"
description: "A sample of completed cinema, museum, planetarium, and government projects by Magna-Tech Electronic Co."
permalink: "/portfolio/"
---
<div class="page-header">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / Portfolio</p>
    <h1>Portfolio</h1>
    <p class="dek">A sample of completed projects across cinemas, museums, planetariums, education, and government.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="block">
  <div class="wrap">
    <img src="/img/portfolio/team-photo.jpg" alt="Magna-Tech team at a project site" class="team-photo">
    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      {% for p in portfolio.entries %}
      <div class="portfolio-card">
        <span class="tag">{{ p.category }}</span>
        <h3>{{ p.name }}</h3>
        <p class="loc">{{ p.location }}</p>
        <p>{{ p.about }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top:2rem;">
      This is a representative sample, not the complete project list. We have hundreds more,
      many for cinemas across Russia and the CIS through our regional partner network —
      ask us about a specific region or venue type.
    </p>
    <p><a class="btn" href="/contact/">Discuss Your Project</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
